# CSS Styling Patterns

## Design System

### Color Palette
- **Primary Orange**: `#fc9` - Main brand color
- **Secondary Pink**: `#f9c` - Complementary brand color
- **Accent Green**: `#9bad97` - Borders and navigation
- **Main Background**: `#1b1b1b` - Primary dark background
- **Shoe Black**: `#080808` - Deepest black for contrast
- **Primary Text**: `#ccc` - Light gray for main text
- **Form Text**: `#20cf9d` - Bright green for form input text
- **Link Blue**: `#6da7f9` - Primary link color
- **Button Purple**: `#c9f` - Primary button background
- **Success Green**: `#20cf9d` - Success states
- **Error Red**: `#ff4444` - Error states

### Typography
- **Oswald** - Brand font for headings and POWERBACK branding
- **Inconsolata** - Monospace for forms, technical content, UI elements
- **Inter** - Modern sans-serif for specific UI components
- **Red Hat Text** - Secondary sans-serif for terms and legal content

### Border Radius
- Small elements: `4px` (buttons, inputs)
- Medium elements: `5px` (cards, modals)
- Large elements: `8px` (sections, containers)
- Circular elements: `50%` (avatars, icons)

### Box Shadows
- Subtle shadows: `0 0 7px rgba(153, 204, 255, 0.5)` (modals)
- Button shadows: `-1px 2px 0px #ccc` (default), `0px 1px 1px #ccc` (hover)
- Email shadows: `4px 6px 0px #080808` (3D button effect)
- Inset shadows: `inset 0 0 5px #cf9` (form inputs)

### Border Patterns
- Primary borders: `2px solid #9bad97` (navigation, sections)
- Form borders: `1px solid #c9f` (inputs), `2px solid #3c3c3b` (search)
- Modal borders: `3px solid #ccccccaf` (headers), `1px solid #9bad97` (body)
- Button borders: `2px solid #080808` (default), `1px solid #fc9` (checked states)

## CSS File Organization

### Co-location Pattern
Keep CSS files co-located with components:

```
components/
  alerts/
    StyledAlert/
      StyledAlert.tsx
      style.css
```

### CSS Modules (for new components)
**REQUIRED for new work**: Use CSS Modules (`Component.module.css`) for new components to prevent selector leakage. Migrate legacy files opportunistically.

```typescript
import styles from './style.module.css';

<div className={styles.container}>
```

**Key Rules**:
- Keep only design tokens, resets, and utility classes in global CSS
- Everything else should be local (module-scoped)
- Use CSS variables for theme tokens at `:root`
- Maintain one stylesheet per component
- Avoid deep shared files except for tokens/utilities
- For conditional styling, keep logic in TSX and toggle module classes (no CSS-in-JS)

### Global Styles
- Use global CSS only for design tokens, resets, and utilities
- Keep component-specific styles in co-located CSS files
- Use CSS custom properties for theme values
- Respect `prefers-color-scheme` for theme tokens

## Bootstrap + Custom CSS Blending

### Core Principle
Use Bootstrap for structure and utilities, custom CSS for branding and interactions.

### Bootstrap Usage
- Layout: `row`, `col`, `d-flex`, `container`
- Spacing: `p-*`, `m-*`, `px-*`, `py-*`
- Responsive utilities: `d-none`, `d-lg-block`, `d-md-flex`
- Component classes: `btn`, `form-control`, `modal-*`, `alert-*`

### Custom CSS Usage
- Brand colors and gradients
- Custom interactions and animations
- Component-specific styling
- Typography customization
- Responsive design beyond Bootstrap breakpoints

### Implementation Pattern
```html
<!-- Combine Bootstrap classes with custom CSS -->
<button className="btn btn-primary custom-button">
  Click Me
</button>
```

```css
/* Custom CSS for branding */
.custom-button {
  background: #c9f;
  border: 2px solid #080808;
  box-shadow: -1px 2px 0px #ccc;
}

.custom-button:hover {
  background: hsl(270, 100%, 77%);
  box-shadow: 0px 1px 1px #ccc;
}
```

## CSS Property Ordering

### Standard 9-Category Hierarchy
1. **Layout**: `display`, `position`, `top`, `right`, `bottom`, `left`, `z-index`
2. **Flex/Grid**: `flex`, `flex-direction`, `flex-wrap`, `align-items`, `justify-content`, `grid-*`
3. **Spacing**: `margin`, `padding`, `width`, `height`, `max-width`, `max-height`
4. **Visual**: `background`, `border`, `border-radius`, `box-shadow`, `opacity`
5. **Typography**: `font-family`, `font-size`, `font-weight`, `line-height`, `text-align`, `color`
6. **Colors**: `color`, `background-color`, `border-color`
7. **Transforms**: `transform`, `transition`, `animation`
8. **Interactive**: `cursor`, `pointer-events`, `user-select`
9. **Media**: `@media` queries

### Example
```css
.component {
  /* Layout */
  display: flex;
  position: relative;
  z-index: 1;
  
  /* Flex */
  flex-direction: column;
  align-items: center;
  
  /* Spacing */
  margin: 1rem;
  padding: 1.5rem;
  width: 100%;
  
  /* Visual */
  background: #1b1b1b;
  border: 2px solid #9bad97;
  border-radius: 5px;
  box-shadow: 0 0 7px rgba(153, 204, 255, 0.5);
  
  /* Typography */
  font-family: 'Inconsolata', monospace;
  font-size: 1rem;
  color: #ccc;
  
  /* Transforms */
  transition: all 0.15s ease-in;
  
  /* Interactive */
  cursor: pointer;
}
```

## Responsive Design

### Breakpoint System
- **Mobile Portrait (Small)**: `max-width: 379px`
- **Mobile Portrait**: `max-width: 599px`
- **Mobile Landscape**: `min-width: 600px`
- **Tablet Landscape**: `min-width: 900px`
- **Desktop**: `min-width: 1200px`
- **Big Screen**: `min-width: 2000px`

### Mobile-First Approach
```css
/* Base styles (mobile) */
.component {
  padding: 1rem;
  font-size: 0.875rem;
}

/* Tablet and up */
@media (min-width: 900px) {
  .component {
    padding: 1.5rem;
    font-size: 1rem;
  }
}

/* Desktop and up */
@media (min-width: 1200px) {
  .component {
    padding: 2rem;
    font-size: 1.125rem;
  }
}
```

## Component-Specific Patterns

### Button Styling
```css
.button {
  /* Layout */
  display: inline-block;
  
  /* Spacing */
  padding: 0.5rem 1rem;
  
  /* Visual */
  background: #c9f;
  border: 2px solid #080808;
  border-radius: 4px;
  box-shadow: -1px 2px 0px #ccc;
  
  /* Typography */
  font-family: 'Inconsolata', monospace;
  font-size: 1rem;
  color: #000000;
  
  /* Transforms */
  transition: all 0.15s ease-in;
  
  /* Interactive */
  cursor: pointer;
}

.button:hover {
  background: hsl(270, 100%, 77%);
  box-shadow: 0px 1px 1px #ccc;
}

.button:active {
  background: hsl(270, 100%, 82%);
  border-style: inset;
}

.button:focus {
  box-shadow: 0 0 0 0.25rem #ffcc9940;
}
```

### Form Input Styling
```css
.form-input {
  /* Layout */
  display: block;
  width: 100%;
  
  /* Spacing */
  padding: 0.5rem;
  
  /* Visual */
  background: #080808;
  border: 1px solid #c9f;
  border-radius: 4px;
  
  /* Typography */
  font-family: 'Inconsolata', monospace;
  font-size: 1rem;
  color: #20cf9d;
}

.form-input:focus {
  background: #0a0a0a;
  border-color: #fc9;
  box-shadow: inset 1px 1px 2px 1px #cc99ff26;
  outline: none;
}

.form-input:invalid {
  border-color: #ff4444;
  color: #ff4444;
}
```

### Modal Styling
```css
.modal {
  /* Layout */
  position: fixed;
  z-index: 1050;
  
  /* Spacing */
  padding: 0;
  
  /* Visual */
  background: #1b1b1b;
  border: 3px solid #ccccccaf;
  border-radius: 5px;
  box-shadow: 0 0 7px rgba(153, 204, 255, 0.5);
}

.modal-header {
  border-bottom: 1px solid #9bad97;
  padding: 1rem;
}

.modal-body {
  padding: 1.5rem;
}
```

## Interactive States

### Hover Effects
```css
.link:hover {
  color: #8bbbfd;
  text-decoration: none;
}

.button:hover {
  background: hsl(270, 100%, 77%);
  box-shadow: 0px 1px 1px #ccc;
}

.image:hover {
  filter: brightness(90%) contrast(106%);
  transition: filter 0.15s ease-in;
}
```

### Focus States
```css
.form-input:focus {
  box-shadow: inset 1px 1px 2px 1px #cc99ff26;
}

.navigation-link:focus {
  box-shadow: 0 0 0 0.25rem #ffcc9940;
}
```

### Active States
```css
.button:active {
  border-style: inset;
  transition: border-style 0s;
}

.image:active {
  padding: 2px;
}
```

